        <h2 class="font-bold mb-4" style="font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.25rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;">
          Ready to Launch and Grow<br />Your Brand in Dubai?
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:1rem;max-width:28rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;line-height:1.7;">
          Get a tailored proposal with clear deliverables, timeline, and budget options.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="/marketing/contact"
            class="px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-105"
            style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7B2FF7,#F72585,#E8A030);font-size:0.9375rem;"
          >
            Request Proposal
          </a>
          <a
            href={waHref}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all hover:border-white/30"
            style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:0.9375rem;"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
